vote.title: Authorize a three-year cooperative purchasing agreement for application and hosting services and ongoing technical and maintenance support for the GovTechCloud and KinetechCloud Program and Claims Management System for the Office of Community Care and Empowerment with Carahsoft Technology Corporation through The Interlocal Purchasing System (TIPS) agreement - Not to exceed $202,741.77 343,263.06 - Financing: Data Services Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
